BEGIN_PGML
(Not randomizable) Use long division to find the quotient and remainder when

[```
            x^4 -25          ```]

is divided by

[```
            x^2-1.
           ```]

The quotient is [_]{$quot}{10}

The remainder is [_]{$remainder}{10}

END_PGML

